339b08","tid":1841081,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"產地?"},{"pid":"518f692b89e29855d4cfa5582d4ad6b90e955618","tid":1841081,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Kq8WEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Kq8WEz.jpg&h=629b609c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e408cd91d5d8b894356195818708de3f1f9ac034","tid":1841081,"uid":167931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"邊撚到呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"db97f07fb9a6da775ecb55160860350b56690ed0","tid":1841081,"uid":264988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eokH06q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeokH06q.png&h=69b7c82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c58d3c6164ce1dd0fa60b6d816ce6a87f4d12c","tid":1841081,"uid":289854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"大埔冇😭"},{"pid":"12b1703546bb340e9a090d7f1c52548afbf453a4","tid":1841081,"uid":93072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"有口罩都未必救到命嘅<br />\n我寫咗啲<span style=\"color: pink;\">戴口罩易岀事嘅位</span><br />\n希望大家可以避免<br />\n從而<span style=\"color: red;\">令口罩發揮最大功效</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【口罩文宣】錯誤戴口罩不可保命！戴口罩Do / Don&rsquo;t ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1248bb1f39b250cbc9b2bcf9b5826dc66f5e3253","tid":1841081,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"雖然得BFE   但無罩嘅巴絲都可以入返些少備用"},{"pid":"d1865b4cc635c64d73c0724823fdc4c6da28da66","tid":1841081,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1248bb1f39b250cbc9b2bcf9b5826dc66f5e3253","tid":1841081,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"雖然得BFE   但無罩嘅巴絲都可以入返些少備用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"bfe99.9喎 上面有圖"},{"pid":"52b2b2194c0c5f4c42d905b7efc78b3bca792bb9","tid":1841081,"uid":110112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"致成屋都係口罩<br />\n但可能都係無用既我們：<br />\n<br />\n[FROM 匿名 醫療從業員]<br />\n<br />\n如何揀口罩<br />\n<br />\n由於條街（特別係藥房）充斥假口罩<br />\n所以打呢篇野比大家參考下<br />\n（如果有醫護發現我篇野有bug歡迎指教...我都驚會搵錯source)<br />\n<br />\n背景：武漢沙士 -&gt; 冠狀病毒<br />\n政府話飛抹傳播（droplet)唔係空氣，咁我地信住先<br />\n跟據網上資料，2003年Sars既virus size大約係0.08-0.14micrometer (10^-6m)<br />\n<br />\n現時有既standard <br />\n<br />\n1. BFE= bacteria filtration efficiency =阻隔細菌 <br />\n<br />\n跟據Nelson laboratory standard, 只可以阻隔 1micrometer既菌 <br />\n結論： 得BFE冇用，因為唔夠細<br />\n<br />\n2. PFE = particle filtration efficiency <br />\n跟據Nelson laboratory standard, 可以阻隔 0.1micrometer既particle<br />\n（醫護用既去到呢個standard, 之後再講 ）<br />\n如果你相信政府，佢係飛抹傳染既話<br />\n呢隻頂到，因為respiratory droplet最細只係去到0.6micrometer，大過bfe既0.1<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;From Dynamics of infectious disease transmission by inhalable respiratory droplets<br />\n<br />\nNikolaos I. Stilianakis and Yannis Drossinos <br />\n<br />\nRespiratory droplets, all droplets generated by an expiratory event&mdash;coughing, sneezing, laughing, talking, breathing&mdash;have diameters d that cover a large size range from approximately 0.6 to more than 1000 &micro;m&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n3. VFE = virus filtration efficiency <br />\n暫時最勁既standard, according to Nelson lab 可以隔到0.027micometer<br />\n呢個size防到舊沙士既virus有突<br />\n我暫時只見到日本某d口罩做到<br />\n<br />\n-結論<br />\n日本野：最少要見到bfe + pfe先好買<br />\n得bfe唔好買 冇用<br />\n有埋BFE+pfe+vfe當然最勁啦 而且都平 （我個人買呢隻）<br />\n<br />\n歐美：ASTM lv 1-3 (3最高） 有咩分別可以睇圖<br />\n都係頂到BFE+pfe<br />\n咁如果中共冇吹水係ok既....<br />\n<br />\n街邊藥房既口罩<br />\n如果英文既有astm lv就係正版啦<br />\n日文野就睇下有冇BFE+pfe+vfe <br />\n冇上面呢兩樣野是但一樣/d日文or英文錯grammar既100%係假野<br />\n<br />\n其他口罩：<br />\nN95<br />\n-可以頂到空氣傳播<br />\n但留意返有分工業用同醫療用<br />\n工業用只係for職安真漢子用<br />\n同埋醫護有做fit test,確保冇air leak先戴得<br />\n漏氣既話=冇用<br />\n所以我唔建議一般人買 因為好焗<br />\n（香港隻nask就ok既 搭飛機可以用 但貴）<br />\n<br />\n防塵/防花粉口罩<br />\n-冇用架咪on9啦<br />\n<br />\n豬咀/其他唔係一次性既口罩<br />\n- 係你除黎洗果下你已經會中啦on9<br />\n- 仲要唔知你識唔識洗<br />\n- 唔識洗既會contaminate埋你洗衣機d衫<br />\n<br />\n產地問題<br />\n大牌子黎講其實大部分made in china<br />\n因為成本問題，醫管局都好多mic野<br />\n但大廠會有qc，所以quality唔會話爭好多<br />\n<br />\n冇經濟能力，搵唔到既<br />\nMade in china都可以照用<br />\n（用日本黎計made in japan個價係mic 4倍)<br />\n<br />\n邊度有得買？<br />\n去屈人寺,萬寧,donki,cosmo搵下啦<br />\n搵唔到就amazon<br />\n但由於日本野唔送海外 所以自己搞轉運啦<br />\n<br />\n補充N95：<br />\n就算N95有用，冇air leak嘅正常配戴設計上都係唔係預人長期帶住用<br />\n帶超過1個鐘就算焗你唔死，長期expose喺病毒之下都係會奶嘢<br />\n所以唔好當N95係萬能，佢只係俾你緊急走難嗰陣用嘅最後一道防線<br />\n<br />\n[From 護士朋友]<br />\n除咗帶口罩，請各位記住<br />\n勤洗手<br />\n洗手洗手洗手<br />\n好L重要<br />\n咪以為帶咗口罩就得<br />\n掂到污染咗患者飛沫嘅物件，再捽眼摸口摸鼻，都係會中<br />\n新年祝大家身體健康🙏🏻"}]}